{"tid":2503734,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺，韓國菜，其實好悶?","createTime":"2021-04-25T10:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T11:40:01.000Z","uid":117802,"like":203,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"804dd3ea4d082bc40db41f6a7cf2fa93333dedd6","tid":2503734,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:09:29.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係嗰十幾款野：<br />\n泡菜，韓式拌飯，韓式炒年糕，韓式烤肉片，韓式燉鍋，韓式炸醬麵 ，韓式燒五花肉，韓式炸雞，冷面 (韓式)，韓式人參雞湯，韓式烏冬，韓式麵，韓式燒肉，韓式蟹，韓式串燒<br />\n<br />\n基本上已經數哂所有韓國菜.....<br />\n<br />\n相比起日本料理嗰種千變萬化，無窮無盡，冇固定形態，無限嘅可能性<br />\n我覺得韓國菜喺款式多樣變化方面，其實其實真係太過狹窄。"},{"pid":"ba4147c6720ea2191df20daade4ad52361ef5111","tid":2503734,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"好單調"},{"pid":"4c0bc57f36439a4a63a7aabc1d7eeecd024c3292","tid":2503734,"uid":38904,"like":55,"dislike":18,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"近代韓狗菜真係畀狗食<br />\n以前韓國有藥膳嗰啲就叫高汁"},{"pid":"2245ebc0a520d6301911de5c79ed99bdddceb6fd","tid":2503734,"uid":117802,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4c0bc57f36439a4a63a7aabc1d7eeecd024c3292","tid":2503734,"uid":38904,"like":55,"dislike":18,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"近代韓狗菜真係畀狗食<br />\n以前韓國有藥膳嗰啲就叫高汁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"韓式藥膳咩嚟"},{"pid":"d8034ec03f2aff8d7177bfdfd50be8c874587e92","tid":2503734,"uid":117802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba4147c6720ea2191df20daade4ad52361ef5111","tid":2503734,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"好單調"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"咩都韓式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7080834e5503c522c94af2dfd1c390221703973b","tid":2503734,"uid":117802,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T10:21:59.000Z","msg":"在首爾市中心高檔的樂天百貨商店(Lotte Department Store)，女售貨員任少羅（Im So-ra，音譯）說，「在首爾，世